Name: Eternal Dungeon
About the game: Descend deep into the Eternal Dungeon - jump, slide and slash your way through to discover what lies hidden within! As you descend deeper into the dungeon, expect more difficult challenges put in place to prevent your path forward! Game Features Fantasy-style cartoon platforming! Nine uniquely themed levels and soundtracks! Colorful hand drawn art style! Over 20 different monsters and bosses with various mechanics! Many spikes and other traps designed to murder you! Steam achievements if you're good enough! Hardcore gameplay designed to test your patience!
